data.title: Anthropomorphic Japan - The Frogs
data.meta_description: Anthropomorphic Japan - The Frogs / compiled by 50 Watts / more details about this series soon! / forthcoming in 2024 from 50 Watts Books
data.text:
Anthropomorphic Japan - The Frogs / vintage illustrations compiled by 50 Watts + collages by Samplerman / 96-page paperback, 5.5 x 8.5 inches, illustrated throughout / a new book series focusing on early-to-mid-20th-century Japanese illustration, drawn from our collection and from archival sources / ISBN 9781957625072 / published April 2024 & now shipping from 50 Watts Books.

Want to place a wholesale order? You can find most 50 Watts publications on Faire, and/or you can email will AT 50wattsbooks.com for a full list (I distribute a few books not on Faire).
